{
  "3167180": {
    "name": "你好！我们还有场恋爱没谈",
    "steam_appid": 3167180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/70afd8c0202784915333205251846577.avif?t=1768469363\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras_big/70afd8c0202784915333205251846577.avif?t=1768469363 width=800 height=336 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/90a57adcd752f4c343b10d91b0e7a951.webp?t=1768469363\" width=253 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《你好！我们还有场恋爱没谈》是一款真人影像互动游戏。在一场突如其来的意外中，你穿越回了18岁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那一年你身上还有劲；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那一年你眼里还有光；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那一年你心里还有梦；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最重要的，那一年……还有她们：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/fc9b4b7914878478ecf3b94dd00e9b1d.poster.avif?t=1768469363\" width=540 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/fc9b4b7914878478ecf3b94dd00e9b1d.webm?t=1768469363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/fc9b4b7914878478ecf3b94dd00e9b1d.mp4?t=1768469363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鼎鼎大名的校园女神 “沈梦萱”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/068ee3ad1fd7523a74ef53073f016a3c.poster.avif?t=1768469363\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/068ee3ad1fd7523a74ef53073f016a3c.webm?t=1768469363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/068ee3ad1fd7523a74ef53073f016a3c.mp4?t=1768469363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >火力全开的拉拉队长“苏笑笑”——CBA御用“蕞红啦啦队”队长“甜不辣”饰演</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/ab017202f374ea5c068e2ce5290fc39e.poster.avif?t=1768469363\" width=540 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/ab017202f374ea5c068e2ce5290fc39e.webm?t=1768469363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/ab017202f374ea5c068e2ce5290fc39e.mp4?t=1768469363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成熟知性的温柔老师“路月如”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/ad0d7c55a9b17138e1942d7b5705967f.poster.avif?t=1768469363\" width=540 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/ad0d7c55a9b17138e1942d7b5705967f.webm?t=1768469363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/ad0d7c55a9b17138e1942d7b5705967f.mp4?t=1768469363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >青梅竹马的邻家女孩儿“楚瑶”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/9b23d50574f7513e4210e09ea8903bb3.poster.avif?t=1768469363\" width=540 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/9b23d50574f7513e4210e09ea8903bb3.webm?t=1768469363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/9b23d50574f7513e4210e09ea8903bb3.mp4?t=1768469363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >霸气高冷的富婆总裁“徐佳佳”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/85013f32f58e26035405897fbb9a54f1.webp?t=1768469363\" width=253 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>首部青春搞笑恋爱互动影游</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“真实细腻的情感成长”、“轻松搞笑的亚洲性喜剧”、“奇幻穿越的爽快感受”，这是我们希望在作品里为您竭力呈现的游戏体验。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富玩法，多样结局</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全流程超过500分钟，二十多个不同结局，和每一个女主之间不止有恋爱时的亲密接触、温暖告白，更有婚后生活的多重展现，最终结局取决于您的选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >影游经典的选项、线索收集、QTE玩法，经过不同的包装，为您带来不同的新鲜体验。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>角色多样，贴合人设</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >五位高颜值女主不同人设性格和外貌特点，总有一款满足您的“初恋回忆”。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更有多种隐藏成就，解锁精彩美女写真、限定公开视频、彩蛋故事线……等待您的探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/e019d6e2e05b123faa4665d78d075594.webp?t=1768469363\" width=253 height=61 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“后来我终于知道，它并不是我的花，我只是恰好途经了它的盛放。”</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“初恋”是深藏在每个人心中的珍贵回忆，那些学生时代的情窦初开、年少时的憧憬幻想，纯真而热烈；那些求而不得、错失遗憾，轰轰烈烈绽放又在岁月中凋零的“花儿”，偶尔在寂静的深夜涌上心头。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《你好！我们还有场恋爱没谈》的创作初衷，正是希望将这些念念不舍，却又因为时间、距离、现实而不得不忘却的珍贵回忆，以另一种形式呈现给玩家。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“念念而忘”工作室由4名拥有十多年游戏行业经验的老兵组成。2023年底立项，起得很早，走得却很慢。这一年里，最大的挑战来自两方面：一是抵御浮躁的市场，沉下心来创作一款纯粹的、能引起人情感共鸣的影游——我们经历过galgame的经典时代，希望作品以新的形式、在有限尺度内同时满足“爽感”与“共鸣”；二是影视专业的跨领域，真人拍摄和游戏动画制作之间存在着不小的鸿沟——幸运的是，我们找到了志同道合的影视制作伙伴，他们曾创作过“t1”级别的影游作品，又在我们这个项目里增加投入了影视剧级别的制作班底。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为“恋爱系列三部曲”（初恋、热恋、失恋）的第一部，《你好！》可能是青涩和不完美的，但我们会努力探索互动影游未来的更多可能——相对于经典时代的那些“名作”，互动影游的潜力还远远未发掘殆尽，也期待每一个玩家的关注支持、批评指教。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“只要活着，悲伤就会逐渐累积。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但我们想做的，就是记录下那些让人温暖的东西。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167180/extras/b13632717b4535b1ae5fa43919a55434.webp?t=1768469363\" width=253 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ1群：1001023124（已满）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ2群：190200357</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B站：你好我们还有场恋爱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抖音：你好我们还有场恋爱没谈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >微博：你好我们还有场恋爱没谈</p>",
